arStrings.szText: Well, Sihek? The Council awaits your word.
(sighs) The Dregs are growing unchecked. They spread throughout the Undercity. Their disease is more virulent than ever before. A child has already died as a result...and she will not be the last.
I am infected. Day by day, it only gets worse. I should have ended my life the moment I realized. Instead, I tried to outrun fate. I was a fool.
Untrue. Your courage and tenacity have been seen by all. You should not have hidden your affliction from us...but we do not condemn you for it.

From now on, you will be Guardian of the Undercity. You will keep this city safe with your insight, and you will continue searching for a cure. You have done well, Sihek, and you are more valuable to us than you know.
I...I accept the Councilâ€™s judgment. Thank you, Ormus.
